OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FNew UK Army chief issues   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FRussia rallying cry        
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The new head of the British Army has   
OL,6, issued a rallying cry to troops -      
OL,7, telling them they need to be ready to  
OL,8, face Russia on the battlefield.        
OL,10,FGen Sir Patrick Sanders, who started   
OL,11,Fthe job last week, addressed all ranks 
OL,12,Fand civil servants in an internal      
OL,13,Fmessage on 16 June, seen by the BBC.   
OL,15,FRussia's invasion of Ukraine shows the 
OL,16,Fneed "to protect the UK and be ready to
OL,17,Ffight and win wars on land", he says.  
OL,19,FHe adds the Army and allies must now be
OL,20,F"capable of...defeating Russia".       
